{"tid":1642480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解從來無人分化藍絲","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T13:00:33.000Z","uid":155477,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2f7b01cf3927a217777d40236ff8c6e668908c","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JO9x63U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJO9x63U.jpg&h=fe3b91c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假AC黎 mon po 狗唔洗特登去搵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個grp 名係 Save HK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/393490971355994/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F393490971355994%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX51cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=d78cd935\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/393490971355994/</a><br />\n<br />\n人數都唔少 入grp要申請但無乜審查<br />\n<br />\n不如大家入去幫手分化下<br />\n<br />\n講下我自己觀察<br />\n<br />\n1.基本上係得藍絲講嘢 佢地無條件支持警察 但政府高官就未必<br />\n<br />\n2. 用番Facebook提供既圖 再打字 最多人like<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAGP9kZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAGP9kZ.jpg&h=bcf1d95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2ySnF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2ySnF6.jpg&h=8e3a61d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己建議係入grp後 可以主打親情牌<br />\n<br />\n範文如下:<br />\n因為這次反送中運動 我同我14歲女兒反面了<br />\n之前佢好痴身 依家成個月無同我講過野 食飯都特登行開[喊喊emoji]<br />\n林鄭同班高官 我一世都唔會原諒你[嬲嬲emoji]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為要分化佢地同警察 幾乎無可能<br />\n<br />\n但要進一步分化藍絲同政府 就有可能 呢個係個潛伏咗係個grp 一個幾月既觀察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地分化唔到藍/警 但如果政府頂唔住黃藍既壓力 第一個搵邊個祭旗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於唔同分化手法 有待聰明既連登仔自行發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2aae6ec0d5cf7daae74464378f7d64bb3845e1","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:25:07.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0b35080f6663f76394d60667472fc9cff876f356","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1e2b42cdcc9ba206aa5063e4c35eab7ae285e8c9","tid":1642480,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"114944ff49ec82dbef957c54ebd3bef5b3188de3","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:26:05.000Z","msg":"就觀察所得<br />\n<br />\n班藍絲係無腦撐警<br />\n<br />\n但唔係無腦撐政府<br />\n<br />\n要分化藍/政 係有可能的"},{"pid":"b057d1a398e3e4b0a442c58e781514bfeb50e1e3","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:26:55.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f7aedd9efe0787e20c6d28211ea0a07c2388a635","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"16df357692c6b4122d0b5bae68f800eec29b03ab","tid":1642480,"uid":36774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"係咪需要重開"},{"pid":"63d421102f7182333eb1ff5992c499990996ff95","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16df357692c6b4122d0b5bae68f800eec29b03ab","tid":1642480,"uid":36774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"係咪需要重開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"重開咩"},{"pid":"e7a35f866a7c0ff9ee1dfe26a0205ebd93dbc8f5","tid":1642480,"uid":68868,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:30:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲咁撚蠢好難分化。"},{"pid":"15a9f171ccf70cb3c36154b2805bad6dbd1fdc0a","tid":1642480,"uid":155477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7a35f866a7c0ff9ee1dfe26a0205ebd93dbc8f5","tid":1642480,"uid":68868,"like":2